data.description: If you need lots of space this is the home for you. This 5 bedroom 2 bath brick ranch has so much to offer you need to see it for yourself!! Great open floor plan includes 2 dining areas, multiple living spaces, over side island in the kitchen, huge pantry/laundry room combination, 3 bedrooms located on the 1st floor, 2 bedrooms located upstairs with sitting/guest space, covered patio with access from owner's suite and family room great for entertaining, detached 20x24 garage with window unit, newly installed above ground pool, privacy fence, and so much more.
